bindsym Mod4+Shift+r move to workspace reddit; workspace reddit
bindsym Mod4+Shift+c move to workspace code; workspace code
bindsym Mod4+Shift+d move to workspace dev; workspace dev
bindsym Mod4+Shift+q move to workspace www; workspace www

